<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=yes">
    <title>✨青春探测仪 · 20题摸清人格✨</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #ffe9f4 0%, #ffe0f0 40%, #f9e6ff 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 16px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border-radius: 48px 24px 48px 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 45px -12px rgba(255, 120, 160, 0.35), 0 6px 18px rgba(255, 200, 220, 0.5);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 700px;
            padding: 32px 28px;
            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff80ab, #b57cff);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        h1 span {
            background: #fff0f5;
            padding: 5px 16px;
            border-radius: 60px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #b45f9b;
            border: 1px solid #ffb6d9;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: #a64d79;
        }

        .subhead {
            color: #b95b9e;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            padding-left: 8px;
            border-left: 6px solid #ffb0d0;
            font-size: 1.15rem;
        }

        /* 进度条 */
        .progress-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: baseline;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #ac5f8b;
        }

        .question-number {
            background: #ffe2f0;
            padding: 6px 20px;
            border-radius: 60px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            border: 1px solid #ffb7cf;
        }

        .progress-bg {
            background: #ffd9e8;
            height: 16px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            margin: 10px 0 25px 0;
            border: 1px solid #ffb2c9;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .progress-fill {
            height: 100%;
            width: 5%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff8eb5, #cb9eff);
            border-radius: 30px;
            transition: width 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 0 8px #ffa5c7;
        }

        /* 题目区域 */
        .question-box {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
            border-radius: 40px 18px 40px 18px;
            padding: 28px 22px;
            margin: 20px 0 32px 0;
            border: 2px solid white;
            box-shadow: 0 12px 25px -15px rgba(255, 120, 180, 0.4);
        }

        .question-text {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.4;
            color: #3a2a35;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            word-break: break-word;
        }

        .options {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .option-item {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 50px 16px 50px 16px;
            border: 2px solid #ffbfd7;
            padding: 14px 22px;
            transition: 0.2s;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px #ffe2f0;
        }

        .option-item:hover {
            background: #fff2f9;
            border-color: #ff96c2;
            transform: scale(1.01);
        }

        input[type="radio"] {
            appearance: none;
            -webkit-appearance: none;
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            border: 2px solid #ff96c2;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-right: 18px;
            position: relative;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.1s;
            background: white;
        }

        input[type="radio"]:checked {
            background: #ff80b0;
            border-color: #ff4090;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px #ffe2f0 inset;
        }

        .option-text {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.4;
            color: #33202a;
            font-weight: 500;
            flex: 1;
        }

        /* 导航按钮 */
        .nav-buttons {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 25px;
        }

        button {
            background: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 60px;
            padding: 16px 28px;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ac4985;
            border: 2px solid #ffb7d5;
            box-shadow: 0 7px 0 #ffbed9;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.08s linear;
            flex: 1;
            text-align: center;
            backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        }

        button:active {
            transform: translateY(5px);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 0 #ffa7c9;
        }

        button:disabled {
            opacity: 0.4;
            transform: none;
            box-shadow: 0 7px 0 #ffbed9;
            pointer-events: none;
            border-color: #ffdbec;
        }

        #nextBtn {
            background: #ffd3e6;
            color: #9f3f73;
            border-color: #ff8bbe;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        /* 结果页 */
        .result-area {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 40px 18px 40px 18px;
            padding: 32px 24px;
            border: 2px solid white;
        }

        .result-badge {
            background: #ffecf2;
            border-radius: 60px;
            padding: 12px 22px;
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: 3px solid #ffbed0;
            color: #a1336b;
        }

        .result-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 30px;
            padding: 28px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 0 #ffbed9;
            border: 2px solid #ffb2cf;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .result-card h3 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #ff6f9d, #b462d6);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .tag {
            background: #fbe4ff;
            border-radius: 40px;
            padding: 8px 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #a84378;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 12px 0 16px;
            border: 1px solid #e2b0ff;
        }

        .statistics {
            background: #ffeef6;
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 18px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #572b46;
            margin: 20px 0 10px;
            border: 1px dashed #ff9fc7;
        }

        .restart-btn {
            background: #d9b0ff;
            border-color: #b96bff;
            color: #381c48;
            box-shadow: 0 7px 0 #b78bff;
            margin-top: 12px;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            padding: 18px;
        }

        .footer-note {
            color: #ad6989;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 28px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        /* 手机优化 */
        @media (max-width: 500px) {
            .card { padding: 20px 16px; }
            h1 { font-size: 1.9rem; }
            .question-text { font-size: 1.3rem; }
            .option-item { padding: 12px 16px; }
            .option-text { font-size: 1rem; }
            button { padding: 14px 16px; font-size: 1.1rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="card" id="app">
    <h1>🔮 青春探测仪 <span>20题摸清隐藏人格</span></h1>
    <div class="subhead">✨ 按真实第一反应选，别思考“应该” ✨</div>

    <!-- 答题区 -->
    <div id="quizSection">
        <div class="progress-row">
            <span class="question-number" id="questionCounter">第 1 / 20 题</span>
        </div>
        <div class="progress-bg">
            <div class="progress-fill" id="progressFill" style="width: 5%;"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="question-box">
            <div class="question-text" id="questionText">加载题目中...</div>
            <div class="options" id="optionsContainer"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="nav-buttons">
            <button id="prevBtn" disabled>⬅️ 上一题</button>
            <button id="nextBtn">下一题 ➡️</button>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-note">🌸 选完才能看报告哟 🌸</div>
    </div>

    <!-- 结果区 (初始隐藏) -->
    <div id="resultSection" style="display: none;">
        <div class="result-area">
            <div class="result-badge" id="resultTypeTitle"></div>
            <div class="result-card" id="resultDescription">
                <!-- 动态插入分析内容 -->
            </div>
            <div class="statistics" id="statisticDisplay"></div>
            <button class="restart-btn" id="restartBtn">✨ 再测一次 ✨</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script>
    (function() {
